ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a95c8efa980eef3adfe5a3f84e2b6ea4244a71","tid":457350,"uid":47250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把人嚴重過你 調整心態會好過d</blockquote><br />\n次次有人有皮膚問題都有d 仆街講呢句，而家又唔係鬥慘，係唔係要等到最嚴重先講得？"},{"pid":"5fc6223eccac7fd8d3ab8364978de8bcf3be4a13","tid":457350,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2點半仲都仲痕到訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇咩方法可以斷尾，比皮膚病折磨左幾十年</blockquote><br />\n樓主可唔可以講下你既飲食習慣, 性格, 作息果d來聽下<br />\n同埋之前中醫師講咩呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經完全介哂海鮮，牛羊，果仁果啲毒野。平時就好相語唔會有脾氣，但係一痕就會燥。作息就日日都11-12點上床訓，但係痕就會訓唔著。</blockquote><br />\n要完全戒凍飲戒甜野"},{"pid":"c11dec7572356c15166232e34a8a76d9e84aeacd","tid":457350,"uid":147241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"我都濕疹左4年係塊面度 唔起濕疹塊面都會好痕 睇左好多中醫西醫都搞唔掂 成千銀皮膚科都睇左幾次 一唔搽類固醇發到豬頭丙咁 最近睇左個西醫 雖然有食到類固醇有搽 但搽左4日冇搽 而家成個月塊面都冇痕過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a302e23f5d75a22d77f19c98f64fccf8d48f1139","tid":457350,"uid":109759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"戒色養身 食中藥 會好反"},{"pid":"fa4bcb4a91832e392734b444c34b20c59ca46da8","tid":457350,"uid":3682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"試下用強力無比膏止痕，幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8438cf51352bacf94599efadab50a4afdabb61c","tid":457350,"uid":80393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"中藥食耐d就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主加油"},{"pid":"af8d8fefca2ab4ac89fd1bdc491d5fae1b455a0f","tid":457350,"uid":72932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"認真 用呢隻藥膏 一搽即刻止痕同埋冇咁紅 之前塊面濕疹 冇你咁大範圍 不過嚴重好多 爛到血淋淋咁 搽左幾枝 而家好番哂 最緊要夜晚敷住佢 如果嚴重到血淋淋可以同凡士林一齊用 傷口會快啲好 同埋唔會乾到裂開<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/123604_534fcff9d3cd6469e9e46bebdbc6685a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F123604_534fcff9d3cd6469e9e46bebdbc6685a.jpg&h=66717964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藥房賣50蚊度"},{"pid":"ed581f5fd5ed4fb65b9f1269410811822d7d3dcc","tid":457350,"uid":29544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"有睇開醫生嘅話就聽醫生話啦<br />\n有類固醇就用類固醇搞掂咗條頸先<br />\n之後搵潤膚膏搽 大大pat咁撻落去 <br />\n撻撻下就會好㗎啦<br />\n過程係有啲漫長 但係呢個係我用咁多個方法最有效而且最信得過嘅一個<br />\n<br />\n咪撚聽啲人話唔好信西醫同用佢地啲偏方<br />\n嗰啲人除咗話西醫治標唔治本同呀邊個用呢條方醫好咗就冇第二句 根本就冇根據 淨係會畀假希望你唔會幫到你"},{"pid":"26bddadadee05f616c99b0990353680b032dd1a8","tid":457350,"uid":2321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都濕疹左4年係塊面度 唔起濕疹塊面都會好痕 睇左好多中醫西醫都搞唔掂 成千銀皮膚科都睇左幾次 一唔搽類固醇發到豬頭丙咁 最近睇左個西醫 雖然有食到類固醇有搽 但搽左4日冇搽 而家成個月塊面都冇痕過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無戒斷反應，無反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8681820d21cc3b8895f8cbebda0019edea445b","tid":457350,"uid":5929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"咁少事就想死<br />\n我成身都係咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d1b1